attributes.mlflow.spanInputs: {"prompt": "Generate telemetry model-driven configuration for Environment protocol on IOS XR. Server: 172.16.1.20, port: 57000, protocol: grpc no-tls, encoding: json."}
attributes.mlflow.spanOutputs:
"telemetry model-driven
 sensor-group ENVIRONMENT-PROTOCOL
  sensor-path Cisco-IOS-XR-telemetry-model-driven-oper:environment/protocol
 !
 destination-group DG-GRPC
  address-family ipv4
   destination 172.16.1.20
    port 57000
    encoding self-describing-gpb
    protocol grpc no-tls
 !
 subscription SUB-ENVIRONMENT-PROTOCOL
  sensor-group-id ENVIRONMENT-PROTOCOL sample-interval 30000
  destination-group-id DG-GRPC
 !"
